{
  "stem": "25912.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother's sister is married to a Frenchman, or was married to a Frenchman, and lived in France.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my mother wrote a little note and asked the French soldier to take it back and post it and tell her that he had seen us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately, he did write a note.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he said he had seen a French-speaking lady.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't mention me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So nobody knew that I was with my mother, and I was alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We got to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was a scene of utter devastation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Most of Warsaw had been bombed during the Warsaw Rising.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when the Rising collapsed in October, the Germans systematically went round, setting fire to the houses which were still standing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So there were very few habitable houses left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We found my grandmother's cook and my grandfather's assistant, butler, or whatever you called him, who lived on the Praga side of Warsaw, where the Russians were in when the Warsaw Rising started.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that part of Warsaw was not involved in the fighting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they gave us shelter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My grandmother's cook put us in business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She knew somebody who was making soap.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, you wouldn't want to use that soap, but-- said she can arrange for us to have samples to sell without a deposit, because we had no money.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, my mother wasn't a very good saleswoman, because when she was told that the soap was so wet, it was practically useless, she agreed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] I was better at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it ended sadly, because I left the samples on the windowsill in the sun, and they dried out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The result was that they were unsellable, and that was the end of my sales career.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
